[I] Uniform password-checking interface

[T] checkpassword provides a simple, uniform password-checking interface to
[T] all root applications. It is suitable for use by applications such as
[T] login, ftpd, and pop3d.
[T]
[T] There are checkpassword-compatible tools that support alternate password
[T] databases, secret login names, long passwords, subaccounts, one-time
[T] passwords, detailed accounting, and many other features. Applications
[T] that use the checkpassword interface will work with all of these tools.

[U] https://cr.yp.to/checkpwd.html

